=head1 DESCRIPTION

Describes the domain name system (DNS) records that you must add to the
DNS of your registered domain to validate ownership for an Amazon
Lightsail SSL/TLS certificate.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 DnsRecordCreationState => L<Paws::Lightsail::DnsRecordCreationState>

An object that describes the state of the canonical name (CNAME)
records that are automatically added by Lightsail to the DNS of the
domain to validate domain ownership.


=head2 DomainName => Str

The domain name of the certificate validation record. For example,
C<example.com> or C<www.example.com>.


=head2 ResourceRecord => L<Paws::Lightsail::ResourceRecord>

An object that describes the DNS records to add to your domain's DNS to
validate it for the certificate.


=head2 ValidationStatus => Str

The validation status of the record.



